units           metal
atom_style      atomic
boundary        p p p

read_data       structure.data

pair_style      eam/fs
pair_coeff      * * KAN_potential.eam.fs Ag

neighbor        2.0 bin
neigh_modify    delay 0 every 1 check yes

thermo          10
thermo_style    custom step pe press pxx pyy pzz vol lx ly lz

min_style       cg
minimize        1.0e-10 1.0e-10 1000 10000

write_data      minimized.data